irety.", "In accordance with shared recommendations for the Centers for Disease Control (CDC), Centers", "for Medicare and Medicaid Services (CMS), the Pennsylvania Department of Health (PA DOH)", "and others, we are required to notify you each time there is a change or development in our", "Covid-19 status, including new cases among residents and/or team members. We are also", "required to notify you if we admit a resident with a Covid-19 diagnosis even if they have met the", "criteria for discontinuation of transmission-based precautions.", "According to guidance we continue to perform widespread testing of all team members once per", "week at various times throughout the week. Team members who present with symptoms", "consistent with Covid-19 are taken off the schedule and advised to consult with their clinician. In", "addition, we are testing residents who present with symptoms consistent with Covid-19.", "We\u2019ve been notified that one of our team members in the Villas whom recently worked on the", "Gardens B neighborhood tested positive for Covid-19.", "Therefore, according to guidance from PA DOH, we have moved Gardens B to a YELLOW", "zone. Visitation to Gardens B is immediately suspended and our team members have", "implemented the appropriate infection control protocols for yellow zones. Visitation to all other", "neighborhoods remains open.", "Since November 2020, we have had a total of 55 residents and 80 team members at the Villas", "test positive for Covid-19. We have also had six third party health care workers who provide", "services to our residents test positive for Covid-19. Furthermore, we have admitted eleven", "residents who have tested positive and had met the criteria for discontinuation of transmission-", "based precautions upon admission and one resident from elsewhere on campus who tested", "positive.", "If you have any questions regarding this communication or St Paul\u2019s plan of action please", "contact Tammy Lininger, Administrato